`•`| **kick ― KICKS THE MENTIONED USER**

- (~kick <@user> <reason>) -

`•`| **ban ― BAN THE MENTIONED USER**

- (~ban <@user> <reason>) -

`•`| **purge ― CLEARS A SPECIFIC AMOUNT OF MESSAGES**

- (~purge <number>) -

`•`| **warn ― WARNS THE MENTIONED USER**

- (~warn <@user> <reason>) -

`•`| **warnings ― CHECKS THE WARNINGS OF THE MENTIONED USER**

- (~warnings <@user>) -

`•`| **clearwarnings ― CLEARS THE WARNINGS OF THE MENTIONED USER**

- (~clearwarnings <@user>) -

`•`| **mute ― MUTES THE MENTIONED USER**

- (~mute <@user> <reason>) -

`•`| **unmute ― UNMUTES THE MENTIONED USER**

- (~unmute <@user>) -

`•`| **userinfo ― GIVES YOU INFO ABOUT A USER**

- (~userinfo <@user>) -

`•`| **botstatus ― GIVES YOU INFO ABOUT THE BOT (UPTIME & MORE)**

- (~botstatus) -

`•`| **urban ― SEARCHES THE URBAN DICTIONARY FOR YOU**

- (~urban <anything>) -

`•`| **stop ― STOPS THE CURRENTLY PLAYING SONG** ***(you cannot use the resume command on this)***
